elf-Portrait of a Gay Reader"; an essay by Christopher Bram on gay writing; and an essay by Joan Nestle on lesbian writing. 0aAuthors, Americany20th centuryvPortraits. 0aGay authorszUnited StatesvPortraits. 0aGays' writings, AmericanxHistory and criticismxTheory, etc. 0aHomosexuality and literaturezUnited States. 0aGayszUnited StatesxIntellectual life. 0aLesbianszUnited StatesvPortraits. 0aGay menzUnited StatesvPortraits. 0aGaysvLiterary collections.07aSchriftsteller.2swd07aHomosexualität.2swd07aBiographie.2swd 7aUSA.2swd 7aIllustrated works.2lcgft 0aPortraits. 7aLiterature.2lcgft  aBaker & TaylorbBKTYc50.00d37.50i0262071800n0002923245sactive  aBaker & TaylorbBKTYc32.00d24.00i0262571250n0003142027sactive  aBrodartbBRODn52602338c$25.00  aBaker and TaylorbBTCPn96047002  aYBP Library ServicesbYANKn1506392  aC0bWAU